{"title":"Discord 互動式按鈕","uid":"1f7de450cd17e95e05f914d2319cc34d","slug":"discord-interactive-button","date":"2021-08-26T23:53:52.000Z","updated":"2022-12-27T04:46:32.114Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/discord-interactive-button.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.ibb.co/k5L4hcN/discord-cover.jpg","content":"<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p>此文案是從我的 Gitbook 搬運過來的，現在它不再被使用。</p>\n</div>\n<p>最近 Discord 推出了一個新功能，就是互動式按鈕，就是一個<strong>根據機器人所發的訊息後，所執行的相關操作</strong>，現在我們可以藉 <code>discord.py</code> 實現互動式按鈕了。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"安裝-discord-components\"><a href=\"#安裝-discord-components\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 discord-components\"></a>安裝 discord-components</h1><p>首先，在編寫程式之前，我們需要安裝並更新 <code>discord component</code> 的 <code>pip</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">pip install --upgrade discord-components</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>需要 Python 版本為 3.6 或以上，方可安裝。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"為程序匯入資源庫\"><a href=\"#為程序匯入資源庫\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"為程序匯入資源庫\"></a>為程序匯入資源庫</h1><p>現在，我們需要在程式中匯入數個資源庫，包括 <code>DiscordComponents</code>、<code>ComponentsBot</code> 以及 <code>Button</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">from discord_components import DiscordComponents, ComponentsBot, Button</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"執行-DiscordComponents-函數\"><a href=\"#執行-DiscordComponents-函數\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"執行 DiscordComponents() 函數\"></a>執行 DiscordComponents() 函數</h1><p>匯入完成後，便要呼喚執行 <code>DiscordComponents()</code> 函數，用以初始化 <code>Discord</code> 元件。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">client &#x3D; commands.Bot(command_prefix &#x3D; &quot;&#x2F;&quot;, intents &#x3D; intents)\nDiscordComponents(client)</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"實現互動式按鈕\"><a href=\"#實現互動式按鈕\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"實現互動式按鈕\"></a>實現互動式按鈕</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"構建互動式按鈕模型\"><a href=\"#構建互動式按鈕模型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"構建互動式按鈕模型\"></a>構建互動式按鈕模型</h2><p>要把互動式按鈕顯示出來，需要用到 <code>components</code> 內的 <code>Button</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">components &#x3D; [\n    Button(label &#x3D; &quot;xxx&quot;)\n]</code></pre>\n\n<p>例如我們想輸入 <code>/send</code> 指令後，機器人會發送一段訊息和一個互動式按鈕。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">@client.command()\nasync def send(ctx):\n    await ctx.send(\n        &quot;Hello World&quot;,\n        components &#x3D; [\n            Button(label &#x3D; &quot;Click me&quot;, custom_id &#x3D; &quot;btn1&quot;)\n        ]\n    )</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p><code>label</code> 為互動式按鈕所顯示的文字。<br><code>custom_id</code> 為互動式按鈕的編碼。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"編寫互動式按鈕點擊事件\"><a href=\"#編寫互動式按鈕點擊事件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"編寫互動式按鈕點擊事件\"></a>編寫互動式按鈕點擊事件</h2><p>好了，互動式按鈕出來了，可是這沒有任何互動啊，這樣我們要編寫互動的程序，<strong>承接以上編碼，繼續編寫</strong>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">components &#x3D; [\n    Button(label &#x3D; &quot;Click me&quot;, custom_id &#x3D; &quot;btn1&quot;)\n]\ninteraction &#x3D; await client.wait_for(&quot;button_click&quot;, check &#x3D; lambda i : i.custom_id &#x3D;&#x3D; &quot;btn1&quot;)\nawait interaction.send(content &#x3D; &quot;Clicked!&quot;)</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p><code>wait_for</code> 是接受 <code>check</code> 參數，是<strong>等待執行點擊按鈕後的事件</strong>，而這裏的 <code>check</code>，是使用了 <code>lambda</code> 方式實現。<br><code>content</code> 是點擊互動式按鈕後所顯示的訊息。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<p>那就大功告成了。</p>\n","text":" 最近 Discord 推出了一個新功能，就是互動式按鈕，就是一個根據機器人所發的訊息後，所執行的相關操作，現在我們可以藉 實現互動式按鈕了。 首先，在編寫程式之前，我們需要安裝並更新 的 。 現在，我們需要在程式中匯入數個資源庫，包括 、 以及 。 匯入完成後，便要呼喚執行 函...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Discord 開發","slug":"Discord-開發","count":4,"path":"api/categories/Discord-開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Python.json"},{"name":"終端機指令","slug":"終端機指令","count":6,"path":"api/tags/終端機指令.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D-discord-components\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安裝 discord-components</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%82%BA%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%8C%AF%E5%85%A5%E8%B3%87%E6%BA%90%E5%BA%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">為程序匯入資源庫</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C-DiscordComponents-%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">執行 DiscordComponents() 函數</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E4%BA%92%E5%8B%95%E5%BC%8F%E6%8C%89%E9%88%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">實現互動式按鈕</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\